source.name: Corvallis Gazette-Times index 7-1-1969 through 11-30-1999
source.description:
An index of articles, obituaries, letters to the editor, and other notable news items published in the Corvallis Gazette-Times newspaper over a 30-year period.

Most records include a date, page number, and column number (or column range). In records with attributes like "illustration" a 0 indicates the absence of an attribute, and a 1 indicates its presence.

Most newspaper content was added to a 3x5" card file, but some (1988 onwards) was added to a spreadsheet. Because different information was captured in each format, the records in this merged index are not homogenous.

This resource would not exist without the dedicated work of our library volunteers.
